                  <p class="ia-table-text">There may be additional costs incurred by heat suppliers due to the need to be compliant with regulations and to address any compliance and enforcement issues raised by Ofgem. These costs have not been included as they are highly uncertain and would be avoidable through compliance with the regulatory requirements. </p>
